## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible strategies for enhancing children's emotional intelligence. The lack of peer-reviewed academic studies in the search results limits the depth of scientific validation. Additionally, the effectiveness of these strategies can vary based on individual child differences and environmental factors. Further research and longitudinal studies could provide more comprehensive insights into the long-term impact of these strategies on children's emotional development.

